=== Dependencies for Torrtux ===
* perl >= 5.10 (for given/when statements)
* xclip

*** The following perl modules (all available on CPAN) ***
* LWP
* HTML::TreeBuilder
* AppConfig
* Term::ANSIColor
* LWP::Protocol::https (optional, useful for some proxies)
* XML::RPC (optional, for subs)
* IO::Uncompress::Gunzip (optional, for subs)
